comment: Two equivalent expressions for double restricted existential uniqueness, analogous to ~ 2eu8 . Curiously, we can put ` E! ` on either of the internal conjuncts but not both. We can also commute ` E! x e. A E! y e. B ` using ~ 2reu7 . (Contributed by Alexander van der Vekens, 2-Jul-2017.)
